    • valueOf

      public static Tag valueOf(String tagName, String namespace, ParseSettings settings)
      Get a Tag by name. If not previously defined (unknown), returns a new generic tag, that can do anything.

      Pre-defined tags (p, div etc) will be ==, but unknown tags are not registered and will only .equals().

      Parameters:
      tagName - Name of tag, e.g. "p". Case-insensitive.
      namespace - the namespace for the tag.
      settings - used to control tag name sensitivity
      Returns:
      The tag, either defined or new generic.
